content:
Story-line => 4/5 (The plot was unique and interesting but it got some loose ends. );
Acting => 5/5 (The voice acting was well-synced.);
Directing => 5/5 (Can't praise the directing enough. I had to wait till the end to see the stories unfold.);
Animation => 5/5 (The animation was soothing, sometimes unbelievable if I consider that it was released in 1986);
Screenplay => 4/5 (The characters were portrayed nicely. But I could have been better);
Personal Recommendation => 5/5 (I would recommend everyone to watch this movie. It will leave you thinking about some important things in your life at the end.);
Most Favorite Character => Dola(The most mature and the kindest character of the whole movie. It might not seem like this in the beginning. But, when the movie ends, you will get to understand what I am saying.);
